<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id" class="dark">
<%- include('layout/head', { title: 'Tentang ShiroHub' }) %>
<body>
    <%- include('layout/navbar', { active: 'about', query: null }) %>
    
    <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-6">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-white text-center mb-6">Tentang ShiroHub</h1>
        
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-[#141b2d] border border-[#1a2338] p-8 space-y-6">
            <div>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white flex items-center gap-2">
                    <img src="/shiroicon.jpg" alt="ShiroHub" class="h-8 w-8 rounded-full">
                    ShiroHub
                </h2>
                <p class="text-[#c8d0e0] mt-2 leading-relaxed">
                    ShiroHub adalah platform streaming anime gratis yang terinspirasi dari 
                    <strong class="text-[#ec4899]">Aplikasi Mobinime</strong>. Dibangun ulang dengan tampilan 
                    lebih segar dan performa ringan.
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 pt-4 border-t border-[#1a2338]">
                <div>
                    <h3 class="font-semibold text-white">Teknologi</h3>
                    <ul class="text-sm text-[#8a9abb] space-y-1 mt-2">
                        <li>• Node.js + Express</li>
                        <li>• EJS (Server-Side Rendering)</li>
                        <li>• Tailwind CSS</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="font-semibold text-white">Fitur</h3>
                    <ul class="text-sm text-[#8a9abb] space-y-1 mt-2">
                        <li>• Streaming episode</li>
                        <li>• Jadwal rilis</li>
                        <li>• Pencarian anime</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="pt-4 border-t border-[#1a2338]">
                <p class="text-sm text-[#6b7a9a]">
                    Data anime diambil dari <strong class="text-[#ec4899]">ShiroNet API</strong>.
                    <br>Dibuat untuk komunitas anime Indonesia.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
    
    <footer class="border-t border-[#1a2338] mt-10 py-6 text-center text-sm text-[#6b7a9a]">
        © 2026 ShiroHub — streaming anime gratis
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
